{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"9ebc535ea2","title":"一切革命斗争都是为着夺取政权","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"cd076759e8","index":0,"year":1933,"month":9,"day":6,"articleId":"9ebc535ea2"}],"tags":[{"id":"c20d333791","name":"关键人物文稿","type":"文稿大类"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wansui2","name":"毛泽东思想万岁(1943-1949卷)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"未知","files":"/books/wansui2a.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wansui2":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"27d402fd83","type":"title","text":"一切革命斗争都是为着夺取政权","index":0,"publicationId":"wansui2","articleId":"9ebc535ea2"},{"id":"23c09ea395","type":"paragraph","text":"世界上一切革命斗争都是为着夺取政权，巩固政权。而反革命的拚死和革命势力斗争，也完全是为着维持他们的政权。","index":1,"publicationId":"wansui2","articleId":"9ebc535ea2"},{"id":"c1ef68c01d","type":"paragraph","text":"革命的阶级一工农劳苦群众，用苏维埃这个武器去对付国内外一切反革命，这就是苏维埃第一个作用。因为必须战胜了这些反革命，阶级才能成为统治的阶级，政权才能成为统治的政权。","index":2,"publicationId":"wansui2","articleId":"9ebc535ea2"},{"id":"f2868174d0","type":"paragraph","text":"（“今年的选举”，《红色中华》第一○八期，一九三三年九月六日）","index":3,"publicationId":"wansui2","articleId":"9ebc535ea2"}],"page":{"id":"84729989f7","publicationId":"wansui2","articleId":"9ebc535ea2","start":289,"end":289}}}},"__N_SSG":true}